item.title: CVE-2022-3843|2024-08-03T01:20:58.761Z -- wago -- unmanaged%20switch%20852-111%2F000-001
item.description: In WAGO Unmanaged Switch (852-111/000-001) in firmware version 01 an undocumented configuration interface without authorization allows an remote attacker to read system information and configure a limited set of parameters.
